{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.1","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:1","prev_osis_id":"Luke.016.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Paroles de J\u00e9sus sur: \u2014 les scandales, \u2014 le pardon des offenses, \u2014 la puissance de la foi, \u2014 les serviteurs inutiles<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. Mt 18:6-9, 21-35. (1 Co 8:9-13; 10:32.) Mc 11:22-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    J\u00e9sus dit \u00e0 ses disciples: <span class=\"wj\">Il est impossible qu\u2019il n\u2019arrive pas des scandales; mais malheur \u00e0 celui par qui ils arrivent!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.2","name":"Luc 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.16.31","name":"Luc 16:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.16.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.2","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:2","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il vaudrait mieux pour lui qu\u2019on m\u00eet \u00e0 son cou une pierre de moulin et qu\u2019on le jet\u00e2t dans la mer, que s\u2019il scandalisait un de ces petits.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.3","name":"Luc 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.1","name":"Luc 17:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.3","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:3","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Prenez garde \u00e0 vous-m\u00eames.<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Si ton fr\u00e8re a p\u00e9ch\u00e9, reprends-le; et, s\u2019il se repent, pardonne-lui.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.4","name":"Luc 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.2","name":"Luc 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.4","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:4","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et s\u2019il a p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre toi sept fois dans un jour et que sept fois il revienne \u00e0 toi, disant: Je me repens, tu lui pardonneras.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.5","name":"Luc 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.3","name":"Luc 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.5","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:5","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Les ap\u00f4tres dirent au Seigneur: Augmente-nous la foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.6","name":"Luc 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.4","name":"Luc 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.6","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:6","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et le Seigneur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Si vous aviez de la foi comme un grain de s\u00e9nev\u00e9, vous diriez \u00e0 ce sycomore: D\u00e9racine-toi, et plante-toi dans la mer; et il vous ob\u00e9irait.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.7","name":"Luc 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.5","name":"Luc 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.7","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:7","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-10: cf. Ro 11:35, 36. Ga 3:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Qui de vous, ayant un serviteur qui laboure ou pa\u00eet les troupeaux, lui dira, quand il revient des champs: Approche vite, et mets-toi \u00e0 table?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.8","name":"Luc 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.6","name":"Luc 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.8","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:8","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne lui dira-t-il pas au contraire: Pr\u00e9pare-moi \u00e0 souper, ceins-toi, et sers-moi, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que j\u2019aie mang\u00e9 et bu; apr\u00e8s cela, toi, tu mangeras et boiras?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.9","name":"Luc 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.7","name":"Luc 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.9","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:9","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Doit-il de la reconnaissance \u00e0 ce serviteur parce qu\u2019il a fait ce qui lui \u00e9tait ordonn\u00e9?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.10","name":"Luc 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.8","name":"Luc 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.10","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:10","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Vous de m\u00eame, quand vous avez fait tout ce qui vous a \u00e9t\u00e9 ordonn\u00e9, dites: Nous sommes des serviteurs inutiles, nous avons fait ce que nous devions faire.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.11","name":"Luc 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.9","name":"Luc 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.11","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:11","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les dix l\u00e9preux<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-19: cf. Lu 5:12-14. Mt 8:2-4. 2 R 5:1-15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, se rendant \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, passait entre la Samarie et la Galil\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.12","name":"Luc 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.10","name":"Luc 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.12","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:12","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Comme il entrait dans un village, dix l\u00e9preux vinrent \u00e0 sa rencontre. Se tenant \u00e0 distance, ils \u00e9lev\u00e8rent la voix, et dirent:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.13","name":"Luc 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.11","name":"Luc 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.13","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:13","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, ma\u00eetre, aie piti\u00e9 de nous!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.14","name":"Luc 17:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.12","name":"Luc 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.14","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:14","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>D\u00e8s qu\u2019il les eut vus, il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Allez vous montrer<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">aux sacrificateurs.<\/span> Et, pendant qu\u2019ils y allaient, il arriva qu\u2019ils furent gu\u00e9ris.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.15","name":"Luc 17:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.13","name":"Luc 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.15","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:15","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>L\u2019un d\u2019eux, se voyant gu\u00e9ri, revint sur ses pas, glorifiant Dieu \u00e0 haute voix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.16","name":"Luc 17:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.14","name":"Luc 17:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.16","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:16","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il tomba sur sa face aux pieds de J\u00e9sus, et lui rendit gr\u00e2ces. C\u2019\u00e9tait un Samaritain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.17","name":"Luc 17:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.15","name":"Luc 17:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.17","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:17","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, prenant la parole, dit: <span class=\"wj\">Les dix n\u2019ont-ils pas \u00e9t\u00e9 gu\u00e9ris? Et les neuf autres, o\u00f9 sont-ils?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.18","name":"Luc 17:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.16","name":"Luc 17:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.18","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:18","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne s\u2019est-il trouv\u00e9 que cet \u00e9tranger pour revenir et donner gloire \u00e0 Dieu?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.19","name":"Luc 17:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.17","name":"Luc 17:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.19","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:19","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Puis il lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">L\u00e8ve-toi, va; ta foi t\u2019a sauv\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.20","name":"Luc 17:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.18","name":"Luc 17:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.20","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:20","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le royaume de Dieu et l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Fils de l\u2019homme<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20:21: cf. Mc 4:26-29.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Les pharisiens demand\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9sus quand viendrait le royaume de Dieu. Il leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Le royaume de Dieu ne vient pas de mani\u00e8re \u00e0 frapper les regards.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.21","name":"Luc 17:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.19","name":"Luc 17:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.21","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:21","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">On ne dira point:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Il est ici, ou: Il est l\u00e0. Car voici, le royaume de Dieu est au milieu de vous.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.22","name":"Luc 17:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.20","name":"Luc 17:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.22","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:22","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.023,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation \u00e0 la vigilance<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 22-37: cf. Da 9:26. Mt 24:3-42.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Et il dit aux disciples: <span class=\"wj\">Des jours viendront o\u00f9 vous d\u00e9sirerez voir l\u2019un des jours du Fils de l\u2019homme, et vous ne le verrez point.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.23","name":"Luc 17:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.21","name":"Luc 17:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.23","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:23","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">On vous dira: Il est ici, il est l\u00e0. N\u2019y allez pas, ne courez pas apr\u00e8s.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.24","name":"Luc 17:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.22","name":"Luc 17:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.24","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:24","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car, comme l\u2019\u00e9clair resplendit et brille d\u2019une extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 du ciel \u00e0 l\u2019autre, ainsi sera le Fils de l\u2019homme en son jour.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.25","name":"Luc 17:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.23","name":"Luc 17:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.25","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:25","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais il faut auparavant qu\u2019il souffre beaucoup, et qu\u2019il soit rejet\u00e9 par cette g\u00e9n\u00e9ration.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.26","name":"Luc 17:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.24","name":"Luc 17:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.26","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:26","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ce qui arriva du temps de No\u00e9 arrivera de m\u00eame aux jours du Fils de l\u2019homme.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.27","name":"Luc 17:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.25","name":"Luc 17:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.27","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:27","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Les hommes mangeaient, buvaient, se mariaient et mariaient leurs enfants, jusqu\u2019au jour o\u00f9 No\u00e9 entra dans l\u2019arche; le d\u00e9luge vint, et les fit tous p\u00e9rir.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.28","name":"Luc 17:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.26","name":"Luc 17:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.28","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:28","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ce qui arriva du temps de Lot arrivera pareillement. Les hommes mangeaient, buvaient, achetaient, vendaient, plantaient, b\u00e2tissaient;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.29","name":"Luc 17:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.27","name":"Luc 17:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.29","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:29","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">mais le jour o\u00f9 Lot sortit de Sodome, une pluie de feu et de soufre tomba du ciel, et les fit tous p\u00e9rir.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.30","name":"Luc 17:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.28","name":"Luc 17:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.30","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:30","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il en sera de m\u00eame le jour o\u00f9 le Fils de l\u2019homme para\u00eetra.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.31","name":"Luc 17:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.29","name":"Luc 17:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.31","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:31","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">En ce jour-l\u00e0, que celui qui sera sur le toit, et qui aura ses effets dans la maison, ne descende pas pour les prendre; et que celui qui sera dans les champs ne retourne pas non plus en arri\u00e8re.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.32","name":"Luc 17:32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.30","name":"Luc 17:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.32","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:32","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Souvenez-vous de la femme de Lot.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.33","name":"Luc 17:33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.31","name":"Luc 17:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.33","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:33","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Celui qui cherchera \u00e0 sauver sa vie la perdra, et celui qui la perdra la retrouvera.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.34","name":"Luc 17:34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.32","name":"Luc 17:32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.34","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:34","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis, en cette nuit-l\u00e0, de deux personnes qui seront dans un m\u00eame lit, l\u2019une sera prise et l\u2019autre laiss\u00e9e;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.35","name":"Luc 17:35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.33","name":"Luc 17:33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.35","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:35","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">de deux femmes qui moudront ensemble, l\u2019une sera prise et l\u2019autre laiss\u00e9e.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.36","name":"Luc 17:36","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.34","name":"Luc 17:34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.36","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:36","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.017.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">De deux hommes qui seront dans un champ, l\u2019un sera pris et l\u2019autre laiss\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.37","name":"Luc 17:37","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.35","name":"Luc 17:35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.37","label":"","reference":"Luc 17:37","prev_osis_id":"Luke.017.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.018.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.17.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Les disciples lui dirent: O\u00f9 sera-ce, Seigneur? Et il r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">O\u00f9 sera le corps, l\u00e0 s\u2019assembleront les aigles.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.17","name":"Luc 17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.18.1","name":"Luc 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.18.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.17.36","name":"Luc 17:36","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.17.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbf80dc76.98034276');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbf80dc76.98034276\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbf80dc76.98034276","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbf80dc76.98034276'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbf80dc76.98034276\" h